                  <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                  <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                  <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                  <i class="bi bi-star text-secondary"></i>
                </p>
                <p class="mb-3 small">
                  7/259 Collins St<br />
                  <span class="suburb-postcode">Melbourne 3000</span>
